@node INTRODUCTION "introduction"

@{b}Introduction@{ub}

Splitter is smart and secure portable multiplatform utility used to split/join
selected files and directories. Hamming and CRC codes are used to secure
your data encoding and decoding during join and split operations.

@endnode
@node LICENCE "licence"

@{b}Licence@{ub}

